cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.SY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on UAV-enabled wireless networks and their deployment for wireless coverage. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as UAVs are considered as robots in this context. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper proposes algorithms to solve the deployment problems. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper considers wireless coverage and communication. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with the deployment of UAVs as a system.
